<body>
<% if flash[:alert] %>
    <div class="body--flash">
        <div class="flash-container">
            <div class="flash--text">
                <%= flash[:alert] %>
            </div>
            <div class="flash--close">
                <%= image_tag('close-expand.png') %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
<% end %>
<div class="body--about">
    <div class="about-container">
        <div class="about--text">
            <p>Unfound Sounds was created by Michael Todd as part of <a href="http://omahacodeschool.com" target="_blank">Omaha Code School</a> in 2014. He curates vinyl treasure hunts starting on the 1st of each summer month (June through September).</p>
            <p>Albums are hidden in local establishments, and are available for pickup during building or business hours wherever they're hidden. Reach Michael at <a href="mailto:michael@unfoundsounds.com">michael@unfoundsounds.com</a> to offer a hiding place in Lincoln, Omaha or Sioux Falls.</p>
            <p>Follow <a href="http://facebook.com/unfoundsounds" target="_blank">Unfound Sounds on Facebook</a> for more updates.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about--close">
            <%= image_tag('close-expand.png') %>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="body--donate">
    <div class="donate-container">
        <div class="donate--text">
            <p>Unfound Sounds is supported by bands, treasure hunt organizer Michael Todd and other vinyl lovers who donate the records that are hidden in local establishments.</p>
            <p>If you'd like to donate an album or offer a hiding place, please email Michael at <a href="mailto:michael@unfoundsounds.com">michael@unfoundsounds.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="donate--close">
            <%= image_tag('close-expand.png') %>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<header class="header">
    <div class="header--container">
        <div class="header--logo">
            <%= link_to image_tag("unfound-sounds-logo.png"), "/", remote: true %>
        </div>
        <div class="header--title">
            <a href="/"><h1>Unfound Sounds</h1></a>
        </div>
        <nav class="header--navigation">
            <div class="navigation--button about-button">
                <h3>about</h3>
            </div><div class="navigation--button donate-button">
                <h3>donate</h3>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </div>
</header>

<%= yield %>

